Hello {{{Recipient.FirstName}}}

Exhibiting at the MD&M West tradeshow gave us the opportunity to make new connections within the Healthcare industry. We wanted to keep you in the loop with a brief tradeshow recap and virtually share the product folders we handed out during the tradeshow.

If MD&M West taught us anything it is that even though it's possible to get so much done from afar, the value of meeting people face-to-face is even higher. FLEXcon Healthcare had a wonderful time meeting customers, highlighting new products, and understanding customer specific design needs. Looking at prototypes and designs we were able to successfully suggest the right product for the right application. We look forward to continue to grow as your trusted partner in healthcare design.

If you are interested in viewing the product folders we passed out at the show? Click the image below to view the virtual product-line folders.
